	* elt-dirs.c (kpse_element_dirs): Return NULL, not the cwd, if
	we're given an empty string.

	* mktex.opt: Determine VARTEXFONTS here.

	* mktexnam: Move determination of VARTEXFONTS to mktex.opt.

