Sun Dec 29 13:26:09 1996  Karl Berry  <karl@cs.umb.edu>

	* db.c (match, elt_in_db),
	* elt-dirs.c (cached),
	* hash.c (hash_lookup),
	* kpsewhich.c (find_format, TRY_SUFFIX),
	* tex-file.c,
